<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> sakavarṣaṁbulu 10<unclear>95</unclear> nē 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁṭi dakṣiṇāyanasaṁkrāṁtinimitta 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>munaṁdu śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalē<unclear>śva</unclear> 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ra kulōttuṁggarājēṁdracō<unclear>ḍa rā</unclear> 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>jularājyamuna Inuṁgaṁṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ṟitiraḍḍi rathitaragōtramu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>na peggaḍlakoḍuku rēmarāju <unclear>koḍuku</unclear> 
<lb n="8"/>dēvana kūṁtuṟu valyapa Amutunūrira 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍḍi tikkarājukoḍuku cōḍerāju curyya 
<lb n="10"/>Ammanapeggaḍa peṁḍlamu valyasāni jo 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nnalagaḍḍaṁ danayettiṁcina guḍi vallabhē 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>śvaramahādēvara pūjārisūryyaca 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>raṇapaṁḍitulaku reṁḍudēvaralaku 
<lb n="14"/>berasi kha 3 śaṁku pra <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> reṁḍudēvara 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>laku berasi kha 1 śrīkulōttuṁgarā 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>jēṁdracōḍeya rājulaku dharmmā 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>rttamugāṁ juriya Ammana cō 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ḍavallabhēśvaradēvaraku reṁḍakhaṁ 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ḍadīpamulaku Iru<unclear>bū</unclear>ṁṭa ni 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>vēdyamunaku kha 2 na 10 dīni nā 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkasthāyigā bhūmipāluru naḍa 
<lb n="22" break="no"/>paṁgalavaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> Īdharmmuvunaku vighna<unclear>mu</unclear> 
<lb n="23"/>sēsinavāru śrīvāraṇāsi vraccinavā 
<lb n="24" break="no"/>ru gaṁgakaṟtaṁ gavilalaṁ boḍcinavāru 
